{"tid":726643,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"睪丸痺一問","createTime":"2018-07-02T14:43:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T18:30:39.000Z","uid":23719,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b9a5a68ca66c71531d5b5b32763158739833dd54","tid":726643,"uid":23719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T14:43:51.000Z","msg":"頭先喺另外位巴打到搭單問自己問題，諗諗下都係開post問好啲<br />\n<br />\n是咁的，近排左邊睪丸底好唔舒服，稱唔上痛但總之怪怪地咁，似係有小小痺嘅感覺<br />\n初頭以為因為著得多緊身褲（其實一星期先一次），著緊身褲嗰日仲要痺得好緊要，所以諗住唔著就無事<br />\n呢兩日零零星星都有呢種感覺，間唔時喺左下腹深處都好似有牽扯感覺，依家間唔時右邊都有少少痺<br />\n有無巴打知我老友乜事？（好驚影響生育能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n利申：上星期一開始出現徵狀，昨日咁啱頭痛眼痛同發燒（但應該唔關事），聽日諗住睇家庭醫生摸摸底先決定睇唔睇泌尿，<br />\n<br />\n另問st paul泌尿o唔ok?"},{"pid":"28e2f2cf89c92a8782cd29958166b07cdaf59bdc","tid":726643,"uid":42268,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T14:48:54.000Z","msg":"有無叫雞習慣？"},{"pid":"561f0e98e2cdd2cdbba4c3aef62da66812672bcd","tid":726643,"uid":2267,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T16:01:09.000Z","msg":"下世小心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38fbbefab87cd897e2ca587d5214eca989245d98","tid":726643,"uid":26711,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T16:05:47.000Z","msg":"如果係睪丸打kick, 你果粒已經壞死左幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e62c8950cfada5c878cdddcebc942081027f0042","tid":726643,"uid":42403,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T16:08:09.000Z","msg":"打飛機多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"509926a1bc45c37bf7d7ede38eb820248a39764a","tid":726643,"uid":1671,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T16:23:04.000Z","msg":"要切了"},{"pid":"a32d758c6f45804d9b2a6f74b269b47384f42762","tid":726643,"ui