:0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T23:59:50.000Z","msg":"巴打，我都係咁<br />\n每次一灣腰，個丸就會有一兩下址住<br />\n食個抗生素消炎等等，都唔見佢<br />\n最後照埋超聲波，都係原因不明<br />\n醫生話，一係切開佢睇<br />\n我就唔洗了<br />\n平時自己就下，唔好坐低灣咁多腰<br />\n唔痛就算，已經一年有多"},{"pid":"bf638be4ea90ca1e273d98a465937d12a23aca36","tid":726643,"uid":4067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T00:48:02.000Z","msg":"我都會<br />\n企我太耐就會有條根由粒蛋連上條腰到<br />\n要彎腰  坐底先冇事"},{"pid":"25ba6b30d85a4af8491a70418f309846773fa15c","tid":726643,"uid":190928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T00:58:41.000Z","msg":"扭蛋？"},{"pid":"a3b6976fb1612e43c7f6f969aa4a378b5dbed8e5","tid":726643,"uid":26711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T01:30:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果係睪丸打kick, 你果粒已經壞死左幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>如果google啱嘅話，睪丸打kick會有劇痛同好明顯嘅腫脹，但我嗰兩粒表面睇乜事都無，即使觸摸都無明顯痛感</blockquote><br />\n認真問你 醫生話有機會無劇痛 但好罕見<br />\n關係到蛋蛋既 睇下醫生穩陣"},{"pid":"a50034c63ad98196220d4bbf8b3a62d8b45798ea","tid":726643,"uid":26711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T01:30:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇硬粒/硬塊<br />\n<br />\n睇下穩陣喎</blockquote>如果我跟得啲方法啱嘅話，自我觸險完唔覺有任何硬塊及墜落感，但附睪有無發炎就真係未必分到<br />\n<br />\n其實我心入面估係附睪或者睪丸炎，但一切都睇下今日醫生點講先，會上嚟講返等大家知道乜病，下次唔駛好似我咁徬徨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ngood luck &amp; bless u"},{"pid":"0543843ce08c5726d44733e3de4ed7610920b2de","tid":726643,"uid":23719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a50034c63ad98196220d4bbf8b3a62d8b45798ea","tid":726643,"uid":26711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T01:30:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇硬粒/硬塊<br />\n<br />\n睇下穩陣喎</blockquote>如果我跟得啲方法啱嘅話，自我觸險完唔覺有任何硬塊及墜落感，但附睪有無發炎就真係未必分到<br />\n<br />\n其實我心入面估係附睪或者睪丸炎，但一切都睇下今日醫生點講先，會上嚟講返等大家知道乜病，下次唔駛好似我咁徬徨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ngood luck &amp; bless u"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T02:41:18.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇完家庭醫生，佢話感冒有時會令下面發炎，處方咗抗生素，過多幾日睇下點再覆診，跟手寫埋轉介信去睇泌尿科"},{"pid":"7e255d0ed6c696e3f009d611c7237395edae2b27","tid":726643,"uid":23719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T02:43:52.000Z","msg":"順便問下，有無人知何孟澈醫生收費同(籠統咁講)醫術如何<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7efc74345145eac904406c344166ce55818e739","tid":726643,"uid":23719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfcb62fa301b2fbeec0e8c0a6a443793a171bbe3","tid":726643,"uid":32260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T23:59:50.000Z","msg":"巴打，我都係咁<br />\n每次一灣腰，個丸就會有一兩下址住<br />\n食個抗生素消炎等等，都唔見佢<br />\n最後照埋超聲波，都係原因不明<br />\n醫生話，一係切開佢睇<br />\n我就唔洗了<br />\n平時自己就下，唔好坐低灣咁多腰<br />\n唔痛就算，已經一年有多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T02:52:42.000Z","msg":"我自己雖然返寫字樓工，但平時都有定時運動，仲要用得腰多，周不時腰酸，加上有少許舊患唔知關唔關事<br />\n<br />\n近排用張瑜珈墊，個人平訓喺到然後個身摺埋將雙腳拉到過埋頭去拉條腰嘅筋，拉返鬆條腰好多，但又係唔知關唔關今次蛋蛋事<br />\n<br />\n點都好，祝巴打早日康復，其實無咩功能性嘅損傷（性能力、生育能力）已經萬幸"},{"pid":"496841e4baced068a038f345d10cd47c2c554ecf","tid":726643,"uid":23719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf638be4ea90ca1e273d98a465937d12a23aca36","tid":726643,"uid":4067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T00:48:02.000Z","msg":"我都會<br />\n企我太耐就會有條根由粒蛋連上條腰到<br />\n要彎腰  坐底先冇事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T02:54:17.000Z","msg":"我依家坐低訓低或者行路都有嗰種感覺，所以我傾向覺得係發炎多過一啲物理性損傷<br />\n<br />\n希望巴打早日康復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b18accc9e2795dba0ccb39b792383b7a3d702f41","tid":726643,"uid":4067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T05:52:40.000Z","msg":"我見好多巴打睇完醫生就話係精索靜脈曲張<br />\n唔知你係唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98872b45b14fb3013c4e01bfa56b4205cf05bda6","tid":726643,"uid":23719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b18accc9e2795dba0ccb39b792383b7a3d702f41","tid":726643,"uid":4067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T05:52:40.000Z","msg":"我見好多巴打睇完醫生就話係精索靜脈曲張<br />\n唔知你係唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T07:36:17.000Z","msg":"呢樣都有可能，但我平時已經唔多企，唔知點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87862b080dd5bd2641c43864ee9f35069be8d782","tid":726643,"uid":83095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T07:56:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.qiusuoo.com/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.qiusuoo.com%2F2&d=zDxXSmgAPCcaYBr5ZWHAv5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=50860f68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.qiusuoo.com/2</a>"},{"pid":"b06715a134813c35d077b9de879e0c1dd8ecc9a6","tid":726643,"uid":4067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98872b45b14fb3013c4e01bfa56b4205cf05bda6","tid":726643,"uid":23719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b18accc9e2795dba0ccb39b792383b7a3d702f41","tid":726643,"uid":4067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T05:52:40.000Z","msg":"我見好多巴打睇完醫生就話係精索靜脈曲張<br />\n唔知你係唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T07:36:17.000Z","msg":"呢樣都有可能，但我平時已經唔多企，唔知點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T11:46:15.000Z","msg":"希望睇完醫生就冇事啦<br />\n我睇撚左好多次都冇用"}]}